---
// Testimonials limpios
---

<section id="testimonials">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-intro text-center">
      <h2 class="section-title">Lo que dicen nuestros usuarios</h2>
      <p class="section-description">Testimonios reales de personas que confían en nosotros</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-2">
      <div class="card text-center">
        <p class="card-text quote">Simple, efectivo y exactamente lo que necesitaba para mi negocio.</p>
        <div class="author">
          <div class="card-visual author-avatar"></div>
          <strong class="card-title author-name">María García</strong>
          <span class="author-title">CEO, StartupX</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card text-center">
        <p class="card-text quote">La mejor decisión que hemos tomado este año para nuestro equipo.</p>
        <div class="author">
          <div class="card-visual author-avatar"></div>
          <strong class="card-title author-name">Juan Pérez</strong>
          <span class="author-title">CTO, TechCorp</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section-intro {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  
  .section-title {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .section-description {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .card-text.quote {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    position: relative;
    padding: 0;
    font-weight: 400;
    max-width: 90%;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .card-text.quote::before {
    content: '"';
    font-size: 5rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    position: absolute;
    top: -2rem;
    left: -1.5rem;
    line-height: 1;
    opacity: 0.08;
    font-weight: 200;
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
  }

  .author {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid oklch(85% 0.01 80);
    position: relative;
  }

  .author::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -1px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 3rem;
    height: 1px;
    background: oklch(85% 0.01 80);
  }

  .card-visual.author-avatar {
    width: 3rem;
    height: 3rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin: 0 auto 1rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, 
      oklch(90% 0.02 80), 
      oklch(88% 0.02 100), 
      oklch(92% 0.01 60)
    );
    border: 2px solid oklch(95% 0.01 80);
  }
  
  .card-title.author-name {
    display: block;
    color: var(--color-text-dark);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  
  .author-title {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  
  /* Responsive para testimonios */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .grid-2 {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 576px) {
    .section-intro {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    
    .card-text.quote {
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    
    .author {
      padding-top: 0.75rem;
    }
    
    .card-title.author-name {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    
    .author-title {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }
  }
</style>
